        ...####.####...     .######.######.     ###.........###
        .####.....####.     .######.######.     .....#####.....
        .##.##...##.##.     ..####...####..     ...#...#...#...
        ....##.#.##....     #..##..#..##..#     ##.#..###..#.##
        ##.....#.....##     ##....###....##     ####..###..####

    rooms-random.lisp
      places rooms randomly adds corridors to connect

    spiralfoo
      spirals, or something akin. code will require tweaking

    termlbrot
      draws a fractal. code will require tweaking

        make termlbrot && ./termlbrot

    wallwalker.lisp
      random walk to fill in space, plus some doors and more

see also https://github.com/thrig/Game-DijkstraMap
         https://github.com/thrig/Game-TextPatterns
         https://github.com/tsadok/level-generator-perlscripts

